---
source: tests/cli.rs
expression: help
---
Send or accept a friend request according to the current relationship

Usage: add [OPTIONS] <USERNAME>

Arguments:
  <USERNAME>
          Exact username with an optional leading @

Options:
      --yes
          Skip only the final default-No confirmation

      --dry-run
          Complete preflight and show details without changing the friendship

  -h, --help
          Print help (see a summary with '-h')

This command follows Venmo's native relationship semantics: it sends a request for a nonfriend and accepts an incoming request. It never retries automatically. Exit code 3 means the friendship outcome must be verified independently.
